                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d243">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Gautemala</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">President of the United States</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-09-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 14, 1901</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Government and people of Guatemala profoundly deplore the death of the
                    illustrious President McKinley, and cordially and sincerely share the universal
                    mourning of your great Republic with which this country cultivates the closest
                    relations, for which reason Guatemala and its Government grieve and make their
                    own the sorrow which the noble American people suffer.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Manuel Estrada C</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
